posts.post_title: T3 Turkey Red New York Highlanders, Yankees
posts.post_content:
1910-11 T3 Turkey Reds! Popular issue and some of the most beautiful cards ever produced. Here are three of the four Highlanders from the set. Both the Manning and Criger have the tougher and more desirable Turkey Red ad back. Sold in comment section trumps any ongoing negotiations. Cross posted.

Rube Manning SGC 1- $250
Lou Criger PSA 1- $250
